org.gitlab.api

Class GitlabIssue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gitlab.api.GitlabIssue

  • public final class GitlabIssue
extends java.lang.Object
    This class serves as instance of Gitlab component Issue. To create, update, or delete this issue, call create(), update(), or delete() explicitly. This supports query for issues globally or within GitlabProject. See GitlabIssue.Query and GitlabIssue.ProjectQuery respectively. Gitlab Web API: https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/api/issues.html

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  GitlabIssue.ProjectQuery
      This extends GitlabQuery and supports query issues within a GitlabProject with searching scope and range.
      static class  GitlabIssue.Query
      This extends GitlabQuery and supports query global GitlabIssues with searching scope and range.
